In the present paper, we extend the results of\n\\cite{dFH09} still further, to include demi-normal varieties without a\n$\\mathbb{Q}$-Cartier canonical class.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Jun 2015 18:16:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-08"}
